{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805070/extras/screenbound-zoom.gif?t=1731950507\" /><br>Enter the unique world of Screenbound, where your Quantum boy (Qboy)<br>transports you into a weird dual dimensional space that occupies 5D = 3d + 2d.<br><br>Screenbound is a platformer unlike any other. You move in first person view at the same time<br>while playing in 2d on the screen of your Qboy. Mind bending environmental puzzles will force you <br>to test the limits of dimensional space. Your jumping and movements are mirrored - but certain things affect <br>the opposite dimension. Combat is in 2d and you will receive your loot in 3d. <br>Find and explore many hidden areas and weird<br>ideas will be all around you. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805070/extras/screenbound-platform.gif?t=1731950507\" /><br>So how the heck did this happen?<br>Your mom invented the device and you found it in the garage. <br>She was keeping it secret all this time, and other dark secrets start to come out as you delve deeper. <br>You'll find other stuff too. But let's not spoil the plot.<br><br>Screenbound also has a level editor in a traditional 2d style - but here's another twist. It auto-generates<br>the 3d level for you! Just imagine the possibilities.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805070/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731950507","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805070/page.bg.jpg?t=1731950507","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805070/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731950507","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805070/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731950507","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"